'''里约热内卢地铁1号线'''（{{lang-pt|Linha 1 do Metrô do Rio de Janeiro}}）是[[巴西|巴西]]里约热内卢的一条地铁线。<ref name="MTB">{{cite news|title=Metrô do Rio de Janeiro (in Portuguese)|url=http://www.transportes.gov.br/bit/ferro/metro-rj/metrorjestacoes.htm|publisher=''[[Ministry_of_Transport_(Brazil)|Ministry of Transport (Brazil)]]''|date=|author=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100715214301/http://www.transportes.gov.br/bit/ferro/metro-rj/metrorjestacoes.htm|archivedate=2010-07-15}}</ref>

1979年1号线通车。通车时共有5个车站开始运营。它们是Praça Onze、Central、Presidente Vargas、Cinelandia和Gloria。

